-- Srinivasa Hatcheries to Build 3-Megawatt Wind Farm in Karnataka in India
-- B y   B a l d a v e   S i n g h
-- 2010-12-16T01:51:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-16/srinivasa-hatcheries-to-build-3-megawatt-wind-farm-in-karnataka-in-india.html
Srinivasa Hatcheries Ltd., an Indian
company with businesses in poultry and real estate, plans to
spend 179 million rupees ($3.9 million) to build a 3-megawatt
wind farm in Karnataka state, the company said in a statement to
the Bombay Stock Exchange.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Baldave Singh at 
 bsingh35@bloomberg.net  